Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.83,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,In Vienna, two maternity\Nwards sat under
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:06.64,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,one hospital roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:08.55,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The first clinic was run\Nby doctors
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:09.70,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,and students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.14,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The second was run by\Nmidwives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The patients were similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.11,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The death rates were not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.76,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,By 1846, the first clinic\Nwas losing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.44,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,more than one in ten\Nmothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:24.20,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Across the same years, the\Nsecond stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.98,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,under 4%.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.99,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Semmelweis found the\Ndifference in the routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:32.02,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Doctors moved from\Nautopsies to childbirth without
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:35.00,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,effective disinfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.44,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,He required chloride of\Nlime hand disinfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.38,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Mortality fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The evidence worked before\Ngerm theory could
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.39,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,explain why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:46.77,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,That was the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:48.37,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Believing the data meant\Nbelieving doctors had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:49.98,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,been carrying death from\Nthe dead to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.59,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:53.94,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The institution protected\Nits identity longer than
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:56.25,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,it protected the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:00.39,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
